Package: aapa
Title: Anchor-Assisted Pedigree Assignment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sheng", "Luan", email = "luansheng@foxmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: High-throughput full-sib family assignment using known candidate 
    parents and anchor individuals. AAPA combines Mendelian compatibility 
    checking with anchor-based kinship scoring to assign test individuals to 
    candidate families, with built-in confidence scoring and rejection 
    mechanisms for unknown-family detection.
